page.title: 14FAMILY SURVEY
page.content: MY MUM WAS BORN AT THE UNIVERSITY COLLEGE HOSPITAL, LONDON. SHE USED TO LIVE IN A TWO ROOMED FLAT WITH HER MUM AND DAD. MY MUM PREFERS LIVING IN {CORRINGHAM}THAN IN LONDON BECAUSE SHE LIKES THE COUNTRY. SHE USED TO MAKE TABLETS AND NOW SHE WORKS AT THE SCHOOL. SHE LIKES IT BETTER AT THE SCHOOL. MY DAD WAS BORN IN{MANOR PARK,LONDON .HE LIVED IN A TERRACED HOUSE AND IT WAS OLD.IT WAS A 3 BEDROOMED HOUSE AND ALSO IT HAD A CELLAR.MY DAD PREFERS LIVING IN CORRINGHAM BECAUSE OF THE {QUIETNESS}.WHEN MY DAD LIVED IN LONDON HE WORKED AT{STRATFORD}.AT THE MOMENT HE WORKS AT FORDS,DAGENHAM. MY DAD WAS BORN AT HOME IN CANNING TOWN,LONDON.HE USED TO WORK AS A CLERK FOR TATE AND LYLE SUGAR IN LONDON.HE NOW WORKS AT TILBURY DOCKS AS A TRANSPORT MANAGER FOR TATE AND LYLE.
